{
  "stem": "25639.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and I felt that this is better than not having it at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After-- mother didn't have any upper teeth until-- ever, after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- to get back to Braunschweig again, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this hole in the ground that we used, that we called latrine, was-- how shall I describe it?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only about this wide, and it had crude wood, like branches, up, and it connected on top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was built especially for us, and-- so that we could hold on to it only at either end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was too tall to hold onto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was only to keep those bars together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I need to draw you a picture of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- there was a board on which we sat, and that was our latrine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we were not permitted to go to the latrine at night, not in Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this young girl of about 16 years of age, suffering from acute dysentery, rushed to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just couldn't hold herself back anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way, the lagerkommandant saw her through her window, and came out with her whip and whipped her to the ground.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but the girl insisted on going, and she-- she went to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was too weak to hold herself up, and she just drowned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She fell in and drowned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they left her there for three days for us to see what will happen to us if we go to the latrine at night.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And keep her from resting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The sight will never, ever leave my memory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had long days, and I think this sort of summarizes the events in Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
